/** 3 approach to jwt
 * 
 * 
  1. (Best approach in general)
  generate token > set token to the cookies > ensure client and server exchange cookies > on the server verify token.

     
  2. (ok type approach)
  generate jwt > send to the client > store it to the local storage > send the token to the server using header > on the server verify token.
  
  

  3. (firebase authentication approach (best approach for our project)

  already have the token in firebase (client side) > we will send the token to the server using auth header > verify the token
  

 
